Additionally, the paper focuses on object-oriented software and mentions sorting algorithms, which are topics that fall under Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the development of verification tools, which could be relevant to the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-category. Finally, the paper evaluates the usability of AutoProof on standard code, which could be relevant to the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-category.
